---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'; import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro'; import Accordion from '../components/Accordion';
const items=[
 {question:'Neon Glow: Your Mental Reset',answer:'<p>Acts as a lighthouse in the dark, helping you find your way during moments of uncertainty. This layer breaks the anxious loop and gives your mind the immediate calm it needs to stop struggling.</p>'},
 {question:'Neuro-aesthetic Art: Deep Immersion',answer:'<p>Specially crafted visual art captures your focus and holds it. This allows your real feelings to surface from the depths, bypassing the noise of daily stress.</p>'},
 {question:'The Mermaid Archetype: Inner Safety',answer:'<p>Familiar since childhood, these images help the conscious mind relax. By lowering your inner critic and reducing the need for control, they clear the way for intuition and positive change.</p>'}
];
---
<Layout title="Method"><PageHero eyebrow="The S.O.S. Magic Method" title="Your Emotional First Aid" intro="Find out how the Complete Digital Interpretation Books and their Neon Decks work together to support you."/><section class="px-5 pb-20"><div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] soft-ring"><video class="aspect-video w-full object-cover" src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/method.mp4" poster="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/videos/method.png" controls playsinline preload="metadata"></video></div></section><section class="px-5 py-24"><div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2"><div><h2 class="display text-5xl">From Mental Noise to Inner Silence and Clarity in Minutes</h2><p class="mt-6 leading-8 text-white/60">This is your guide to the subconscious depths where your true answers wait.</p><p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-white/60">By reconnecting with your intuition, you reclaim the confidence you need to feel grounded and finally tune into your own frequency.</p></div><img src="https://sosmagic.b-cdn.net/fotos/Photo%2023-02-2026%2C%2015%2056%2006.png" alt="Section 2 visual" class="rounded-[2rem] soft-ring"/></div></section><section class="px-5 pb-28"><div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[.75fr_1.25fr]"><div><p class="eyebrow">Why it works?</p><h2 class="display mt-5 text-5xl">The Three Layers of Your Transformation</h2><p class="mt-6 leading-7 text-white/60">This journey is an effortless, science-backed method designed to bypass mental resistance through three visual layers.</p></div><div><Accordion client:load items={items}/><p class="mt-8 leading-7 text-white/60">The S.O.S. MAGIC Method is more than just cards; it is a tool to tune into your own frequency and reclaim your confidence through the subconscious.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold">Its effectiveness is trusted by our global community of 150,000+ women.</p></div></div></section></Layout>
